{"tid":1009330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港特區護照持有人免簽證前往巴拿馬和亞美尼亞","createTime":"2019-02-05T06:01:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T11:11:43.000Z","uid":82640,"like":9,"dislike":43,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"e7c7a5242421c18abd867e0d861d2da879f883f9","tid":1009330,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:01:33.000Z","msg":"入境事務處今日（二月一日）宣布由二○一九年二月十日起，香港特別行政區（香港特區）護照持有人可免簽證前往巴拿馬旅遊，最長可逗留三十天。巴拿馬國民護照持有人亦可免簽證來港旅遊，最長可逗留三十天。<br />\n<br />\n另外，由二○一九年三月三日起，香港特區護照持有人可免簽證前往亞美尼亞旅遊，最長可逗留一百八十天。亞美尼亞國民護照持有人亦可免簽證來港旅遊，最長可逗留三十天。<br />\n<br />\n入境事務處發言人稱：「巴拿馬和亞美尼亞是『一帶一路』沿線國家。在『一帶一路』倡議下，此互免簽證安排會為香港、巴拿馬和亞美尼亞遊客帶來更大的便利，並有助加強在旅遊、文化和經濟方面的聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n連同巴拿馬和亞美尼亞在內，已有共一百六十五個國家／地區給予香港特區護照持有人免簽證或落地簽證待遇。"},{"pid":"d440b7661f4e55405a35f54894ed3117f70431fc","tid":1009330,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:02:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9406751c719082d3f98dcf054e4a90d35b626f1c","tid":1009330,"uid":20473,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:04:35.000Z","msg":"巴拿馬都係一戴一露<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"449ecdbfb87c5558ab6c5287f9ee862edfe1403a","tid":1009330,"uid":53026,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T06:07:27.000Z","msg":"有交情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbc7df1d8ef519037537543b760f101338f3b1c6","tid":1009330,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":13,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"9406751c719082d3f98dcf054e4a90d35b626f1c","tid":1009330,"uid":20473,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":2,"